 }
}]]></fr:pre><fr:p>The above code first accumulates all the outgoing links from the given tree and any of its children, and then restricts (by intersection) to those with taxon <fr:code>reference</fr:code>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
